autostart.conf

  The default config file for this plugin

com.vdr.autostart.pkla

  A polkit configuration file in case VDR is not started as root and not
  started from X.

  Copy this file to /var/lib/polkit-1/localauthority/10-vendor.d and 
  modify the line Identity=unix-user in case that VDR is not started
  as vdr user.